[06/06/2019 05:43:55] <font color="#ffffff">¡No!</font>
[06/06/2019 05:43:59] <font color="#ffff00">Y es, maravillosamente absurdo.</font>
[06/06/2019 05:44:16] <font color="#0000ff">(M SICA)</font>
[06/06/2019 05:44:19] <font color="#ffffff">Sí lo ganaríamos...</font>
