[06/06/2019 11:13:25] <font color="#00ff00">Dieciocho.</font>
[06/06/2019 11:13:27] <font color="#00ff00">Solo uno más.</font>
[06/06/2019 11:13:27] <font color="#ffffff">Solo uno.</font>
